results.name: a(n) = a(n - a(n-1)) + a(floor(2*n/3)).
mathematica: Clear[a, f, b, c, g] (*fractal noise chaotic sequence*) f[0] = 1; f[1] = 0; f[1] = 1; f[n_] := f[n] = f[n - f[n - 1]] + f[Floor[2*n/3]] (*Cantor like fractal stair step chaotic sequence*) g[0] = 1; g[1] = 0; g[1] = 1; g[n_] := g[n] = g[Floor[2*n/3]] + g[Floor[n/3]]; ListPlot[Table[{f[n], g[n]}, {n, 0, 200}], PlotJoined -> True]; Table[f[n], {n, 0, 200}]
